<H1>Folder Structure & Route Groups</H1>

aerovista/
├─ app/
│  ├─ layout.tsx          # Root layout for entire site
│  ├─ page.tsx            # Home page (index)
│  ├─ (divisions)/        # Route groups for each division
│  │  ├─ skyforge/
│  │  │  ├─ page.tsx      # e.g., SkyForge home
│  │  │  └─ layout.tsx    # Optional layout for that division
│  │  ├─ lumina/
│  │  ├─ nexus/
│  │  ├─ horizon/
│  │  ├─ vespera/
│  │  ├─ summit/
│  │  └─ echoverse/
│  ├─ components/
│  │  ├─ Header.tsx
│  │  └─ Footer.tsx
├─ public/
├─ tailwind.config.js
├─ package.json
└─ ...


layout.tsx: Wraps all pages, sets <html>, <body>, and global theming or components.
page.tsx in root: The new “home page” (index route).
(divisions)/.../page.tsx: Separate pages for each division, using respective accent colors.